### QuizBirr API Testing
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5050/api

### 1. Send OTP (Register/Login)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+251912345678"
}

### 2. Verify OTP (Complete Login)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+251912345678",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### 3. Get Profile (Requires Auth Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Get Quiz Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/quiz/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Get Random Quiz
GET {{baseUrl}}/quiz/random
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 6. Submit Quiz Answer
POST {{baseUrl}}/quiz/submit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "quizId": "quiz-id-here",
  "answer": true
}

### 7. Get Wallet Balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallet/balance
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 8. Get Transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallet/transactions
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 9. Admin - Get All Quizzes (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/quiz/all
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 10. Admin - Create Quiz (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/quiz
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "question": "Is the sky blue?",
  "correctAnswer": true,
  "points": 10,
  "category": "general"
}
